Use the <bold>Delete</bold> button to remove highlighted alerts from the <bold>Alert Pattern List</bold>:


<indent>1.	<indent>Select the alert(s) you want to remove.


</indent></indent><indent>2.	<indent>Click <bold>Delete</bold>. 


A pop-up confirmation box asks you to confirm the delete before <italic>Ishmail</italic> removes the alert from the <bold>Alert Pattern List</bold>.


</indent></indent>§

