<indent><indentright><bold><x-color><param>Blue</param>NOTE:</x-color></bold><indent>  This option differs from the <bold>Save Patterns</bold> option. Though both look for matching patterns in mail headers to decide into which folder a message should be saved, the <bold>Automatic Filing</bold> option does this automatically for new mail arriving in the <bold>InBox</bold> folder, while the <bold>Save Patterns</bold> option is invoked when you select one or more messages to move from one folder to another


</indent></indent></indentright>§

