The <bold>File</bold> list contains the list of files in the current directory. The list is updated each time you enter the name of a different directory in the <bold>Current Directory</bold> text field (and press <fixed>Return</fixed> or press <fixed>Enter</fixed> or click the <bold>Set</bold> button) or when you double-click on a directory in the <bold>Directories</bold> list selection field.


