<Bold><<></Bold> Edit

</Indent>§

[CARD] ishmail.boolExpWin.findAllPB.ctx.HLP
[TITLE] Find All (Complex Search) Button
Click <bold>Find All</bold> to apply the query you have built in the <bold>Query Display Area</bold>. The message list in the <bold>Main</bold> window will be positioned at the first message which meets the search criteria. All messages meeting the search criteria will be selected (highlighted). If no messages meet the criteria, no messages are selected and you will see "No Matches Found" in the message area at the bottom of this window.


