<indent><indentright><bold><x-color><param>Green</param>TIP:</x-color></bold><indent>  You may find it's easier and quicker to use the <bold>Open (Recent)</bold> option or the <bold>Open (List)</bold> option. 


</indent></indent></indentright>When you choose <bold>Open</bold>, <italic>Ishmail</italic> opens the <bold>Select Folders</bold> box, where you specify the mail folder(s) to open. You can open one or more mail folders simultaneously and display the contents of the first folder in the <bold>Folder</bold> contents area.


