The <bold>Folder</bold> contents area displays the contents of the <italic>active</italic> mail folder. Mail messages are represented by envelope or letter icons, depending on whether they have been "read." You can have as many mail messages in your <bold>Folder</bold> contents area as you wish.


For each mail message listed, <italic>Ishmail</italic> shows this information in the columns of the <bold>Folder</bold> contents area:


