[CARD] ishmail.readWin.msgHeadText.ctx.HLP
[TITLE] Heading Area
The heading area displays the header information for the messages. Mail messages frequently contain numerous headers, many of which not of interest to users. With <italic>Ishmail</italic> you can specify which headers to display. To set the default for incoming messages, use the <bold>Options</bold> menu of the main window. 


