</indent></indent></indentright>When you click <bold>Include Signature File</bold> a cascading menu is opened offering you the choice of four possible <fixed>.signature</fixed> files. See the <bold>Signature Preferences</bold> dialog for information about signature files. You may have different signatures for internal mail versus external mail. You may also have plain text and enriched text versions of the internal and external signatures.


