[CARD] ishmail.fileIncFilePB.ctx.HLP
[TITLE] Include/Attach External File Option
When you select <bold>Files(s)</bold> from the <bold>Include/Attach</bold> menu the <bold>Include/Attach File</bold> dialog is opened. This is very similar to the Open Folder dialog. You can enter the path name of one or more files, separated by pressing <fixed>Return</fixed> after each name. Or, click the <bold>Show list</bold> button to see an expanded dialog that lists files in the current directory and subdirectories of the current directory. You can then select a file by clicking on a name in the list.


