To change the name of the default save file or to change other preferences, use the <bold>Preferences</bold> option of the <bold>Options</bold> menu.


<indent><indentright><bold><x-color><param>Blue</param>NOTE:</x-color></bold><indent>  If the <bold><italic>Delete messages after saving</italic></bold> preference is set, the message will be marked as deleted rather than saved. If the <bold>Hide deleted messages</bold> is set, the message will be removed from the message list.


