[CARD] ishmail.boolExpWin.parPB.ctx.HLP
[TITLE] Search Expression - Parenthesis Buttons
 Use the <fixed>(</fixed> button to insert a left parenthesis in your query. Use the <fixed>)</fixed> button to insert a right parenthesis.


Parenthesis are used for grouping expressions to indicate precedence of operators. The following examples show how use of parenthesis can change the results of a search. 


